oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: 13th Annual Nashville Unlimited Christmas Concert (2012)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Concerts; Holidays; Christmas; Pomeroy, Dave; Henry, Don; Neel, Johnny; Peters, Gretchen; Nashville Mandolin Ensemble; Mosser, Jonell; Fund raising;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color window card (dark green, light green, and teal on white) announcing the 13th Annual Nashville Unlimited Christmas Concert hosted by Dave Pomeroy and Don Henry with musical guests Johnny Neel, The Ornaments, Gretchen Peters, Michael "Supe" Granda, the Nashville Mandolin Ensemble, Jonell Mosser, The Gypsy Hombres, and more at Christ Church Cathedral on December 11. Proceeds from this concert benefit Room In the Inn.
